assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Mubarrad Holding Company K.S.C.P., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the real estate, transportation, investment, and other businesses in the State of Kuwait and internationally. It operates through Real Estate; Transportation, Leasing, and Maintenance; and Investment segments. The company buys, sells, and invests in real estate properties. It also engages in leasing, transportation, and maintenance of vehicle and equipment to corporate and individual customers and investments with similar or related operations. In addition, the company invests in properties; leases heavy construction equipment, including tower and mobile cranes, dump trucks, construction hoists, motor graders, wheel loaders, excavators, black hole and skid street loaders, power generators, rollers, air compressors, sand rollers, trailers, and lorry cranes; and engages in the real estate and general contracting activities. Further, it establishes and manages tourist villages; logistics services; and offers specialized services, such as warehousing, inventory management, packaging, and freight forwarding. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Kuwait City, Kuwait. Mubarrad Holding Company K.S.C.P. operates as a subsidiary of A'ayan Leasing and Investment Company K.S.C.P.
